# Commit style

Branch:

```txt
<codename>/<slug>
```

Commit:

```txt
<codename>: <imperative lowercase message>
```

PR title:

```txt
<Codename>: <Title case summary>
```

PR body must include:

- What changed
- Why now
- Owned paths touched
- Approval/proposal link if relevant
- Tests run
- Coordination impact
- Remaining work

Before PR:

```bash
bun typecheck
bun test
```

Adapt commands to the repo’s package manager.
